---
title: Sweet Chili Tofu Sandwiches with Ranch and Side Salad
description: Wing night flavours... in a sandwich! Sweet and sticky chili sauce smothers tender, golden tofu. Spread DIY ranch on the sandwich buns, then dunk garlicky broccoli into the rest as a dip!
